@NODE "Einf" "Introduction"
@TOC "MAIN"
@{i}PatchInterleaved@{ui} is a small Patch, which patches the OS so,
that every new Screen which is opened, has the "Interleaved" flag.
Short: Every Screen will be opened in Chunky-Pixel-Mode.

But the acceleration is only minimal.Because this Patch is so small,
you do not loose Memory!!!

@{"Back" LINK "Main"}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Install" "Installation"
@TOC "MAIN"

Copy @{i}PatchInterleaved@{ui} into the WBStartup-Drawer of your WB.
Then @{i}PatchHidden@{ui} will be startet while every booting.

You should start PatchInterleaved, before the WB-Screen will be opened.
(Add PatchInterleaved to your Startup-Sequence!!!)

@{"Back" LINK "Main"}
@ENDNODE

